General.Name: iShares Expanded Tech Sector ETF
General.Description: The fund generally will invest at least 80% of its assets in the component securities of its underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of its underlying index. A significant portion of the underlying index is represented by securities of companies in the technology industry or sector. It is non-diversified.
